OL,3,CHomeless couple living in bus stop
OL,4,Cafter 'refusing to be separated'
OL,6,FA homeless couple has turned a disused
OL,7,Finto a temporary home, after refusing
OL,8,Fto be separated by the council.
OL,10,FThe site is complete with cupboards,
OL,11,Fchairs, carpet, bins and bedding, and
OL,12,Fthere are even Super Mario Bros-themed
OL,13,Fmakeshift curtains.JSupport charity
OL,14,FTrident Reach said it was working with
OL,15,Fthe couple to find "appropriate
OL,16,Faccommodation" - but said they had so
OL,17,Ffar refused offers.
