OL,3,CHomeless couple living in bus stop
OL,4,Cafter 'refusing to be separated'
OL,6,FOne of those living in the shelter
OL,7,Fsaid they would not accept a move
OL,8,Fwhere it meant they were forced to
OL,9,Fseparate.
OL,11,FThe stop is not in use and is due to
OL,12,Fbe removed.
OL,14,FTransport for West Midlands (TfWM)
OL,15,Fconfirmed the process to knock down
OL,16,Fthe shelter was "underway".
OL,18,FThe demolition process will include
OL,19,Fdisconnecting the power supply,
OL,20,Fsecuring road work permits and
OL,21,Fscheduling work with contractors.
