OL,3,CHomeless couple living in bus stop
OL,4,Cafter 'refusing to be separated'
OL,6,FBirmingham is in the grips of a
OL,7,Fhousing crisis, with more than 23,000
OL,8,Fhouseholds waiting for a property,
OL,9,Fincluding nearly 5,000 households who
OL,10,Fare homeless and living in temporary
OL,11,Faccommodation.
OL,13,FBusinesses in the area claimed the bus
OL,14,Fstop being used as a home was
OL,15,Fattracting "anti-social behaviour"
OL,16,Ffrom large crowds gathering late at
OL,17,Fnight.
OL,19,FOne shopkeeper, who chose not to be
OL,20,Fnamed, said his livelihood was being
OL,21,Faffected.
