OL,3,CHomeless couple living in bus stop
OL,4,Cafter 'refusing to be separated'
OL,6,FHe said: "I've complained to the
OL,7,Fcouncil so many times, but nothing has
OL,8,Fbeen done so far.
OL,10,F"People are scared to visit my shop at
OL,11,Fnight because of the crowds.
OL,13,F"Every night 20 to 25 people gather
OL,14,Fhere. This is bothering my business.
OL,16,F"I'm paying #6,000 in business rates
OL,17,Ffor the year and #20,000 in rent. It's
OL,18,Fa big problem for me - but what can I
OL,19,Fdo?"
