OL,4,Cafter 'refusing to be separated'
OL,6,FAnother shopkeeper said: "It's a very
OL,7,Fsad situation, of course, but the anti-
OL,8,Fsocial behaviour is affecting us and
OL,9,Four customers.
OL,11,F"Something needs to be done so they're
OL,12,Fgiven a proper place to stay.
OL,14,F"It's not fair to anyone what's
OL,15,Fhappening at the moment. We need to
OL,16,Ffind a solution that suits everyone."
