OL,3,CHomeless couple living in bus stop
OL,4,Cafter 'refusing to be separated'
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council confirmed the
OL,7,Fbus shelter on Bristol Road was no
OL,8,Flonger in use for passengers and "will
OL,9,Fbe removed soon", but no date had been
OL,10,Fset.
OL,12,FA council spokesperson said: "Homeless
OL,13,Fsupport services have contacted the
OL,14,Fcouple and made accommodation offers.
OL,16,F"The offers have not yet been taken
OL,17,Fup, but the offer of support and
OL,18,Faccommodation will continue to be
OL,19,Fthere should they change their mind."
