OL,3,CHomeless couple living in bus stop
OL,4,Cafter 'refusing to be separated'
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Trident Reach said:
OL,7,F"Our teams are aware of the couple and
OL,8,Fhave been trying to work with them to
OL,9,Ffind appropriate accommodation.
OL,11,F"Unfortunately they have declined
OL,12,Faccommodation as it is currently not
OL,13,Fin the area they would prefer.
OL,15,F"We will always work with people to
OL,16,Fencourage them into appropriate
OL,17,Fhousing but unfortunately sometimes
OL,18,Fpeople do decline help.
