OL,6,F"We will continue our daily checks on
OL,7,Fthe couple and continue with offers of
OL,8,Fhousing support and options for them."
OL,10,FTrident said staff worked "closely"
OL,11,Fwith police, but was "unaware of any
OL,12,Fconcerns regarding anti-social
OL,13,Fbehaviour".
OL,15,FIt said: "We would always encourage
OL,16,Fanyone concerned about someone
OL,17,Fsleeping rough to report their
OL,18,Fconcerns to us using Streetlink."
