OL,6,FA spokesperson for TfWM said: "All bus
OL,7,Fservices have been consolidated at a
OL,8,Fneighbouring shelter so this one is no
OL,9,Flonger required and it has therefore
OL,10,Fbeen earmarked for removal.
OL,12,F"The process to remove the shelter is
OL,13,Funderway, including disconnecting the
OL,14,Fpower supply, securing road work
OL,15,Fpermits and scheduling the works with
OL,16,Fcontractors.
