OL,6,F"In the meantime, we're liaising with
OL,7,Four partners including the police,
OL,8,Fcouncil and local housing providers
OL,9,Fwho are working to secure suitable
OL,10,Flong-term accommodation for the people
OL,11,Finvolved.
OL,13,F"We thank the local community for
OL,14,Ftheir patience while the issue is
OL,15,Fresolved."
